dBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T14:32:02.000Z","msg":"支國教育係，仇恨教育，崇尚叢林法則，不可組織，不能合作，不是追求真理，只係如何鬥別人。人格扭曲，不求思考，不求正義。（沒有宗教信仰，沒有正確人格教育，沒有正確社會意識，沒有合作信任教育，這些信仰及教育會同共產黨一黨一人統計有嚴重矛盾，所以不會存在）<br />\n支那教育，你只要學習好如何為共產黨貢獻，鬥背晒所有理科書，幫助共產黨管治下的科技發展，幫助共產黨對抗西方就得。"},{"pid":"ac5c5d83ef1d0f054c19a71d323dd6b39d77aef4","tid":2316904,"uid":279326,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T22:03:37.000Z","msg":"唔失既人就睇下當年既上海<br />\n歷史在重演"},{"pid":"bf8c4f10887577a002bac17c9e0f25305cbc4d01","tid":2316904,"uid":352996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T22:04:30.000Z","msg":"有機會就要走"},{"pid":"450e4ca46af21d6d8f02e22bd2e3d3156c648577","tid":2316904,"uid":230146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T22:13:01.000Z","msg":"一早話咗陰d陰d咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d5312dadabc0551cab0e6f692f08b949e8a6ac","tid":2316904,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T22:17:36.000Z","msg":"個別事件姐<br />\n有祖國唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb647fcf81615599a5acb6488e2cc96e56cc10d","tid":2316904,"uid":325346,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T22:20:38.000Z","msg":"公屋窮撚就快讀到男女拔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe817f713316277a48ebfb5dc8d1e42c520f8846","tid":2316904,"uid":83910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T22:20:47.000Z","msg":"有錢自己唔走都要送仔女去外國讀書啦<br />\n<br />\n留係度一陣放學返黎批鬥篤灰父母"},{"pid":"9733e8cb169edd0c027d42524adba89e2afb2269","tid":2316904,"uid":10454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T22:23:33.000Z","msg":"插班女學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a52c1dcb4e3147bc70aa8c976459be22c3f9e4","tid":2316904,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T22:27:27.000Z","msg":"以前通常係中三中四之後先多人走出國"},{"pid":"47966